<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif">
  <h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:24px">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">How does StyleHub Miami work?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">StyleHub Miami lets you search and shop across 5 major retailers (Amazon, AliExpress, Sephora, SHEIN, and Macy's) from one place. Browse products, add them to your cart, and check out securely. We handle order routing and tracking.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">Is my payment secure?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Yes. All payments are processed through Shopify's secure, PCI-compliant checkout. We never store your credit card information. You can also pay with Shop Pay, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and other trusted methods.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">How long does shipping take?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Shipping times vary by product and source. Amazon products typically arrive in 3-7 business days. AliExpress and SHEIN orders may take 7-20 business days. Estimated delivery is shown on each product page.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">How do I track my order?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Once your order ships, you'll receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. You can also track your order from your account page or our <a href="/pages/tracking" style="color:#e53e3e">tracking page</a>.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">What is your return policy?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">We accept returns within 30 days of delivery for most products. Items must be in original condition. Start a return from your account or contact our support team. Read our full <a href="/policies/refund-policy" style="color:#e53e3e">return policy</a>.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">Can I cancel or change my order?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">If your order hasn't shipped yet, contact us immediately and we'll do our best to cancel or modify it. Once shipped, you'll need to wait for delivery and then initiate a return if needed.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">What if my package is damaged or lost?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Contact us within 48 hours of delivery for damaged items. For lost packages, wait until the estimated delivery date has passed, then reach out and we'll investigate with the carrier and arrange a replacement or refund.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">Do you ship internationally?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Currently we primarily ship within the United States. International shipping availability depends on the product source. Check the product page for shipping options to your location.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;cursor:pointer">How do I create an account?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Click "Sign in" in the header. You can create an account using your email (passwordless login) or sign in with Shop. Having an account lets you track orders, manage addresses, and access your order history.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size:14px;color:#888;margin-top:32px;text-align:center">Still have questions? <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#e53e3e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none">Contact our support team</a></p>
</div>

